review: We have not consulted the doctor as we have booked the appointment at 12:30 waited till now and some doctor gave scanning for that also we need to wait for 1:30 mins

Doctor behaviour was good and listened to our problem properly. There was not much waiting time to consult the doctor and everything was good. I would like to give a rating of 4/5 and I'm satisfied with the doctor's treatment.

The hospital had no intimation of my appointment and the doctor was on leave even though it showed on Practo that she’s available. 
Call the hospital directly instead of doing it through Practo

tags: Explanation of the health issue,Doctor friendliness,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
